### User Group CRUD Tests

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:9090
@contentType = application/json

### CREATE - Add new user group
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/user-groups
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Java Beginners",
  "description": "Group for learning Java basics"
}

### GET ALL - Get all user groups
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/user-groups

### GET BY ID - Get specific user group (change ID as needed)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/user-groups/1

### UPDATE - Update user group (change ID as needed)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/user-groups/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Advanced Java",
  "description": "For experienced developers"
}

### DELETE - Delete user group (change ID as needed)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/user-groups/1

### Test 404 - Get non-existent user group
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/user-groups/9999

### Test validation - Create group with empty name
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/user-groups
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "",
  "description": "This should fail validation"
}
